{
  "stem": "21626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And three kittens were born just shortly before we left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I was so afraid my father would have them drowned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And Marta promised that she wouldn't let him drown them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And moreover, she promised she would visit my parents every single day so that they wouldn't miss me too much.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And you know, she did that, even when it was forbidden for non-Jews to mix with Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "In fact, one day, the local policeman visited her parents and said, you know, Marta is placing the whole family in danger by not obeying the laws, the German laws.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You shouldn't let her visit the Diamants as she does.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And her father said, she made a promise to her best pal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And no way am I going to make her break this promise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I so valued what she did when I learned about it after the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Just before we left, our thoughtful parents [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] gave me the most wonderful gifts.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "My father gave me a diary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's a-- it was a leather-bound book full of empty pages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And he told me to write it in when I was lonely or homesick or when I was happy, when I had something of interest to say, so that when I came back home, we could all sit around the table and read the diary together.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And my mother, she carried me on that last night at home to an open window.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I remember the night sky was full of stars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And she said, there may be times when we can't write to one another.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
